OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAfter a chilly start, a dry day
OL,6,Fto follow with variable amounts of
OL,7,Fhigh cloud but also bright spells, the
OL,8,Fskies becoming generally clearer into
OL,9,Fthe evening. Winds mainly light, with
OL,10,Ftemperatures rising above average.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FDry with long clear spells
OL,13,Fand turning chilly again, with a touch
OL,14,Fof ground frost in sheltered spots.
OL,15,FWinds mostly light but becoming
OL,16,Fbreezier along the coast and over
OL,17,Fhills.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
