OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FDry and fine, with long sunny
OL,6,Fspells. Warm or very warm inland but a
OL,7,Fbrisk breeze, especially around
OL,8,Fcoasts, giving a noticeably cooler
OL,9,Ffeel here.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,12,FWednesday, dry and very warm with
OL,13,Fsunny spells. Lighter winds. Thursday,
OL,14,Fcooler and breezy with sunshine and
OL,15,Fshowers. Friday, mostly dry but
OL,16,Fgenerally cloudier with occasional
OL,17,Fbright spells. Breezier later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
